    {
      "start": 142.88,
      "end": 146.96,
      "text": "So obviously we do want to try to avoid any of these major mistakes."
    },
    {
      "start": 147.56,
      "end": 149.92,
      "text": "So after we've done our pattern,"
    },
    {
      "start": 150.12,
