    {
      "start": 242.54,
      "end": 245.94,
      "text": "so that's what we need to kind of improve on as well."
    },
    {
      "start": 245.94,
      "end": 249.04,
      "text": "So I'll just come around to this side."
    },
    {
      "start": 249.04,
      "end": 252.54,
      "text": "So with this one, for colour belts and black belts,"
    },
    {
      "start": 252.54,
      "end": 254.14,
      "text": "it's actually scored a little bit differently."
    },
    {
      "start": 254.14,
      "end": 256.03999999999996,
      "text": "So if you're a colour belt,"
    },
    {
      "start": 256.03999999999996,
      "end": 258.53999999999996,
      "text": "you'll actually, your average,"
    },
    {
      "start": 258.53999999999996,
      "end": 261.24,
