    },
    {
      "start": 302.14000000000004,
      "end": 305.54,
      "text": "So 1.3 would be your average that you start from."
    },
    {
      "start": 305.54,
      "end": 309.94000000000005,
      "text": "So say your power and speed was above average,"
    },
    {
      "start": 309.94000000000005,
      "end": 315.54,
