      "start": 468.34,
      "end": 472.03999999999996,
      "text": "is actually considered pretty good."
    },
    {
      "start": 472.03999999999996,
      "end": 474.84,
      "text": "And anything over a 7,"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.84000000000003,
      "end": 476.84000000000003,
      "text": "is actually considered almost world-class."
    },
    {
      "start": 476.84000000000003,
      "end": 479.84000000000003,
      "text": "So if you get a 7 for any of your patterns,"
    },
    {
      "start": 479.84000000000003,
      "end": 482.24,
      "text": "you generally need to pat yourself on the back"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.24,
      "end": 483.94000000000005,
      "text": "because you did an amazing job."
    },
    {
      "start": 483.94000000000005,
      "end": 487.34000000000003,
      "text": "So we just went through our form day scoring."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.34000000000003,
      "end": 490.94000000000005,
      "text": "So just remember accuracy is a 4.0,"
    },
    {
      "start": 490.94000000000005,
      "end": 493.24,
      "text": "presentation is a 6.0,"
    },
    {
      "start": 493.24,
      "end": 496.64000000000004,
      "text": "accuracy is judged during your pattern,"
    },
    {
      "start": 496.64000000000004,
      "end": 498.64000000000004,
      "text": "presentation is after,"
    },
    {
      "start": 498.64000000000004,
      "end": 502.44000000000005,
      "text": "and then we get the two scores that we add up"
    },
    {
      "start": 502.44000000000005,
      "end": 503.64000000000004,
      "text": "and we get that number."
    },
    {
